<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 15:11:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国对伊朗实施新制裁，针对指挥官和航运</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-hits-iran-with-new-sanctions-targeting-commanders-shipping-2024-02-27/</link><description>美国周二宣布实施制裁，目标是伊朗和胡塞武装指挥官以及一艘向中国企业运送价值超过 1 亿美元伊朗商品的船只。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 14:35:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-hits-iran-with-new-sanctions-targeting-commanders-shipping-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>英国财长与 Shein 主席就伦敦 IPO 进行会谈 - 消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-finance-minister-held-talks-with-shein-chair-about-london-ipo-source-2024-02-27/</link><description>英国政府消息人士告诉路透社，英国财政部长杰里米·亨特已与 Shein 执行主席唐纳德·唐进行了会谈，这家中国创办的快时尚连锁店渴望在伦敦上市。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-finance-minister-held-talks-with-shein-chair-about-london-ipo-source-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪展示了可以漂浮的SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-off-suv-that-can-also-float-2024-02-27/</link><description>中国比亚迪周二在日内瓦车展上展示了其阳王U8，这是一款豪华插电式混合动力SUV，能够在发生水事故时漂浮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:26:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-shows-off-suv-that-can-also-float-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲数据中心努力应对人工智能驱动的空间需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/european-data-centres-grapple-with-ai-driven-demand-space-2024-02-27/</link><description>行业参与者表示，随着人工智能需求的蓬勃发展与有限的扩展可能性相冲突，欧洲数据中心的空间短缺问题正在加剧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 13:13:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/european-data-centres-grapple-with-ai-driven-demand-space-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织部长级会议：阿布扎比会议的关键问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/wto-meeting-abu-dhabi-whats-stake-2024-02-27/</link><description>来自世界各地的部长将于 2 月 26 日至 29 日在阿布扎比召开世界贸易组织 (WTO) 部长级会议，试图为全球商业制定新规则，包括改革争端制度和削减渔业补贴。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 12:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/wto-meeting-abu-dhabi-whats-stake-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国称地方政府必须防止房地产市场波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-local-governments-should-prevent-property-market-volatility-ministry-2024-02-27/</link><description>中国住房和城乡建设部周二在其网站上表示，中国地方政府应帮助平衡房地产市场的供需。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:22:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-local-governments-should-prevent-property-market-volatility-ministry-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，越南从印度进口糙米用于再出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/vietnam-imports-husked-brown-rice-india-re-exports-sources-say-2024-02-27/</link><description>贸易和政府消息人士称，越南几十年来首次从印度进口糙米，用于加工谷物并出口精制白米，河内试图利用全球对糙米的强劲需求获利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:16:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/vietnam-imports-husked-brown-rice-india-re-exports-sources-say-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>彪马旨在在“充满挑战”的市场中提升其品牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/puma-aims-boost-its-brand-challenging-market-2024-02-27/</link><description>德国运动服装品牌彪马周二表示，预计今年上半年在充满挑战的市场中将表现疲软，但其股价小幅上涨，因为该公司坚持一月份设定的年度目标，并宣布了一项新的品牌宣传活动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:11:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/puma-aims-boost-its-brand-challenging-market-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管受到渥太华的审查，中国资金仍在追逐加拿大的重要矿业交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-money-still-chasing-canadian-critical-mining-deals-despite-ottawas-2024-02-27/</link><description>根据阿尔伯塔大学进行的专有研究，加拿大收紧关键矿产行业的外国投资规则一年后，中国资金继续涌入多伦多上市的矿业公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:04:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-money-still-chasing-canadian-critical-mining-deals-despite-ottawas-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中东关注，焦虑的债券受到竞价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-27/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 11:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>研究显示，由于欧洲投资担忧，中国收购量下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/study-shows-dip-chinese-takeovers-amid-european-investment-concerns-2024-02-27/</link><description>审计和咨询公司安永的一项研究显示，中国面临的经济挑战，加上对中国在欧洲投资的谨慎态度，导致去年中国买家在欧洲大陆的收购数量下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:30:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/study-shows-dip-chinese-takeovers-amid-european-investment-concerns-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>印度动力煤进口量自大流行以来首次下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-thermal-coal-imports-seen-falling-first-time-since-pandemic-2024-02-27/</link><description>行业官员周二表示，由于国内产量增加和库存创历史新高，预计今年印度动力煤进口量将出现自 COVID-19 大流行以来的首次下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 10:18:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-thermal-coal-imports-seen-falling-first-time-since-pandemic-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>阿里巴巴旗下南亚电商巨头Daraz在备忘录中宣布裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-south-asian-e-commerce-giant-daraz-announces-layoffs-memo-2024-02-27/</link><description>阿里巴巴旗下的电子商务平台 Daraz Group 代理首席执行官 James Dong 周二在路透社看到的一份致员工的内部备忘录中表示，该公司已宣布在整个集团进行裁员，以“采用更加精简和灵活的结构”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:49:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/alibabas-south-asian-e-commerce-giant-daraz-announces-layoffs-memo-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>牙科种植体制造商士卓曼对 2024 年持谨慎态度，押注中国增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/dental-implants-maker-straumann-sees-steady-sales-growth-2024-2024-02-27/</link><description>瑞士种植牙制造商士卓曼 (Straumann) 周二预测 2024 年销售额将稳定增长，在长期的经济不确定性中采取谨慎立场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:47:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/dental-implants-maker-straumann-sees-steady-sales-growth-2024-2024-02-27/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国出货量激增，印度四月至一月钢铁进口量创六年新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-apr-jan-steel-imports-six-year-high-china-shipments-surge-2024-02-27/</link><description>路透社周二看到的临时政府数据显示，在中国出货量的带动下，印度钢铁进口量在截至3月份的本财年前10个月触及六年来新高，并且印度是成品钢材的净进口国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 06:43:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-apr-jan-steel-imports-six-year-high-china-shipments-surge-2024-02-27/</guid></item></channel></rss>